data.title: Survival of The Fittest
data.meta_description: Listen to Survival of The Fittest, the new track by Maino featuring August which was dropped on Friday, April 30th, 2010.
data.text:
Check out Survival of The Fittest, the latest from Maino which features a guest appearance from August on the assist. The track was released on Friday, April 30th, 2010. Maino's chances in this game are improving with each new release, and Survival of The Fittest is no exception - quite the opposite, in fact. It's a nice addition to the impressive catalogue Maino has been building over the years. We're definitely anticipating the next move.

Check out Maino on Don't Say Nothin' (Remix), featuring Dirty Money. If you're down, make sure to visit Maino's profile page for the newest info, news, songs, and mixtapes.
